title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: A gold and dark blue ribbon has been tied around the corner post of the fence, and a cluster of small, pink tea roses has been fixed at the knot's center.  At the base of the post, full sunflowers have been laid, intermingled with a varicolored assortment of rose cuttings.
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
